- Summary index to solve slow searches that ensures faster display of dashboard panels. 
    - We have a join command connecting search results from two base searches. 1 of the searches has a large data volume. 
    - We created a summary index for that search to make overall search faster 


- Save as Report to speed up slow searches and load a dashboard panel faster 
    - Run the slow SPL and Save as a Report 
    - Select the frequency of the report 
    - Go to the dashboard where you want the fast panel
    - Click Edit in Top right 
    - Click + Add Panel in the middle left 
    - Select New from Report 
    - Pick the Report you just saved as a panel.
    - Now that Panel should load faster   
